logicFunctions.paramSource:
SELECT f.*
        FROM study_site ss, study_site_protocol ssp, protocol p, facility f
        WHERE ss.facility_cd = ssp.facility_cd 
        AND p.protocol_id = ssp.protocol_id
        AND p.study_id = ss.study_id
        AND ss.facility_cd = f.facility_cd
        AND ss.site_num = ssp.site_num
        AND ss.facility_cd = ssp.facility_cd
        AND ss.study_id = (SELECT study_id FROM study WHERE project_code = '<project_code>')
        AND f.active_ind = 'Y'
        AND ss.screening_ind = 'Y'
        AND ssp.active_ind = 'Y'
        AND ssp.screening_ind = 'Y'
        ORDER BY ss.site_num, ssp.protocol_id;

3 - Sigmoidoscopy - a thin, flexible tube with a camera is inserted through the rectum and used to view the closest section of the colon

3 - Moderate symptoms, but I am managing

Alias: Opt-Out Close 1 Element# QSC9016 We are sorry that you do not wish to remain in Acurian’s database. We want to make sure you know that your privacy has not been compromised in any way, and that we did not receive your information from your doctor or any other health professional. Acurian sends information to people who we believe may be interested in research study opportunities. You may have previously expressed interest in receiving information about this health condition through a survey or on Acurian’s website, or you may have been included in our mailing because of generally available demographic information about you, like your age and gender.

Agent Note: Optional language for CC agents if additional follow-up is necessary: 
Acurian receives information from companies who conduct surveys which include health-related information. It is possible that you filled out one of these surveys at some time in the past, even several years ago, and provided permission to be contacted with information about the health concerns that you reported at that time.It is also possible that you never filled out a survey of this type. Since some medical conditions are more common among certain age groups, you may have been included in a mailing because you live near one of the research centers, and people of your age group and/or gender are more likely to have the condition that is being researched.I would like to assure you again that we have not received any health information about you from your doctor, insurance company, or any other medical professional. If you are concerned about your privacy I can submit a request for someone from Acurian to follow up and let you know exactly where we received your name.

Would you like to be removed from our database at this time?

Alias: Site Contact Close

Element# QSC9025
Thank you again for contacting Acurian's Research Information Center. We will remind the study physician's office of your continued interest in study participation. Goodbye.

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS26
projQuestions.questionText: Alias: General Information Close Element# QSC9026 For more information about Acurian and other clinical research study opportunities, please visit www.Acurian.com. Thank you for contacting Acurian's Research Information Center. Goodbye.

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS27
projQuestions.questionText:
Alias: Warm Transfer Close 1

Element# QSC9027
While I have you on the phone, I would like to try to transfer you to the study doctor’s office so that they can confirm your qualifications and see if they can schedule an office visit. Can you please hold for just a minute while I try to reach the office?

answerChoices.choiceText: 1 - No: Ok no problem, I will pass your information on to the study doctor’s office and they will call you back. They will probably ask you some additional questions over the phone, and may invite you to come into the office for an in-person evaluation. Thank you again for contacting Acurian’s Research Information Center. Goodbye.

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS28
projQuestions.questionText:
Alias: Warm Transfer Close 2 Element# QSC9028 Great, please hold for just a moment. If we should get disconnected for any reason, please do not worry, we will pass your information on to the study doctor's office and they will just get in contact with you directly. [Attempt to call site]

Agent Notes:
Dial the displayed phone number: %SITE_COORDINATOR_PHONE_NUM%
The agent should give the site phone number to the caller, if the caller is requesting it.

If site does not answer - do NOT leave a message

If site answers: 
Hello, this is %OPERATOR_NAME% calling from Acurian. May I please speak to the person in your office who is responsible for scheduling initial patient appointments for the AbbVie Crohn’s disease study? [If the site is unsure about which study you are calling about refer to protocol name and numbers %PROTOCOL_LIST%]

If site not available:
Ok no problem. We will send their RPA over within the next 24 hours and they will be able to call %PATIENT_FIRST_NAME% %PATIENT_LAST_NAME% at a more convenient time.

If available - once on phone:
We have a patient on the line that has passed the Acurian pre-screener and is interested in participating in the AbbVie Crohn’s disease study. You’ll receive their referred patient alert within the next 24 hours, but would you be able to speak with him/her right now and set up his/her first office visit? [If the site is unsure about which study you are calling about refer to protocol name and number %PROTOCOL_LIST%]

answerChoices.choiceText: 1 - Yes: Great, I'll connect them now
2 - No: Ok - we will send their RPA over within the next 24 hours and you can review their qualifications at a more convenient time. Their name is (patient name).

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS29
projQuestions.questionText:
Alias: Warm Transfer Close 3

Element# QSC9029
The site is available to speak with you now. I am going to transfer you over to %SITE_COORD_FIRST_NAME% %SITE_COORD_LAST_NAME%. Thank you again for contacting Acurian’s Research Information Center. Goodbye.

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS30
projQuestions.questionText:
Alias: Warm Transfer Close 4

Element# QSC9030
I apologize, the person that schedules appointments is not available at this time. So I’m going to pass your information on to the study doctor’s office and they will contact you within the next few days. Thank you again for contacting Acurian’s Research Information Center. Goodbye.

projQuestions.caption: Close-QS31
projQuestions.questionText: Element# QSC9031 For Call Center Tracking - Please select one of the following dispositions:

answerChoices.choiceText: 1 - Transfer not attempted - patient not interested in being transferred
3 - Site was contacted but was unable to take transfer call
